World news: Man beheaded in France, Islamic flag found on siteA man has been decapitated during a suspected Islamist terror attack in France.A message in Arabic was reportedly found on the victim's head, which had been pinned to a fence.Two attackers arrived at a gas factory near Grenoble in a car, bearing banners written in Arabic, and set off explosions.Several other people are reported to have been injured.One attacker, who is said to be known to authorities, has been arrested.